	<Title>
		Flat stomach: Can girdles tighten abdominal muscles?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Want a flat stomach? Diet and exercise &amp;mdash; not undergarments &amp;mdash; are what count.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can wearing a girdle help tighten stomach muscles?
	</Question>
